Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們常說 書和電影帶給孩子們的心理影響非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影裡的名作也有許多存在過激的暴力 性描寫的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀後產生了共鳴的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一天就會做出相同的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個想法究竟正確嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 請問是彼布利亞古書堂的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 來捐書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是圖書委員田邊 來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個我也去拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些書不適合給中學生讀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我們不能收下這些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…每一本都是評價很高的文學作品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有性描寫 暴力描寫…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本帶給孩子們的影響比想像中大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如有學生最近讀了這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提交了一篇批判學校體制的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼讀後感？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫當好人的人 成不了真正的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那乾脆作淨惡事才更有人類本色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志田 小菅來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些書 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我準備的 看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？今天好文靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在煩妹妹的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫結衣 今年中學二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹不和了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 其實她偷東西被抓到 停學了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說在DOWN TOWN RECORD偷了八張CD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八張？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 而且是同樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去了BOOK PALACE賣錢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問為什麼做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟本不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 這種時候該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹的事情你最清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼頭緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前還寫了一篇奇怪的讀後感 引發問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說 有點叛逆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是篇寫得相當好的作文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得了東慶報的讀後感作文比賽的最優秀獎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的讀後感作文比賽也每年受到表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比其他人寫的好多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 我和大哥就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自豪的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇讀後感導致媽被叫去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量讀後感 小題大做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹的學校叫聖櫻女學館 校規出了名地嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 姐現在去那邊捐書了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「讀『發條橘子』有感」 二年一班 小菅結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀完這本書 我立即去聽了貝多芬的第九交響曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它在書中出現過好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子比我想像中要長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後合唱的部分非常美 讓我歡呼雀躍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買它的時候還不知道書中講的什麼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為會有機械和水果登場 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道竟然一樣都沒有 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人公艾力克斯說著奇怪的詞語 淨幹壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論做了什麼都不反省 成天和同伴們聊音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕被警察抓住 進了監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也保持著壞人的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有一天他被洗腦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了絕對幹不成壞事的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過即便成了好人 艾力克斯也過得不幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前欺負過的人回過頭來欺負他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他卻保護不了自己 喊道「我簡直是發條橘子啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只能按照規定地方式行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者彷彿在說 哪怕逼迫一個人去當好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果他也成不了真正的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…乾脆作淨惡事才更有人類本色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 在醫院裡艾力克斯又被洗腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新變回了壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是追求名望的大臣在利用艾力克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇小說裡沒有一個真正的好人出場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾力克斯能袒露心聲的對象只有音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在病房裡聽著最愛的貝多芬第九交響曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾力克斯開始想像地球高聲慘叫的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也側耳傾聽著這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想…說不定可以聽見地球的慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 父母當然會擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大輔看過『發條橘子』？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你看不了書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很激進的內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激不激進的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑社會加土匪 強暴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人公無法無天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小孩子看的書啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者並不是在煽動犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是描寫出惡夢般 無可救藥的社會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是作者用心的反面描寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟每個人都有好奇心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種故事產生共鳴也情有可原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這孩子不僅僅是想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂而皇之地寫成讀後感 交給學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學生就這樣 今後長大了怎麼樣可想而知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷東西也是受了這本書的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道偷東西的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你聽見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹在哪兒找到的『發條橘子』？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我網上訂購的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說去看了車站附近的書店 沒貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以結衣托我買
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEPSON 太明朝體Ｂ\b0\fscx62\fscy77}刊{\r}子姐還要去聖櫻女學館？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接到老師的幾張訂單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去送書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯幫我看看結衣的情況嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天停學處分解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣最近在學校怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼奇怪的地方？我想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去取錢 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菅啊 臉皮真厚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧她可以面不改色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然偷東西 人渣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很缺錢用麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菅主動承認錯誤 道過歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在反省了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼布利亞古書堂有圖畫書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然不放到店面上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人賣我們噢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我圖書委員的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個月有一次圖畫書的朗讀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朗讀？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東鎌倉小學和巖谷小學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是心想如果有好書 可以請你告訴我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朗讀的時候 我挑幾本借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友開心我也開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊和小菅結衣是朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們倆都喜歡看書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常一起去古書店買書喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 可以來上學太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是彼布利亞古書堂的店主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她姐姐奈緒經常光臨小店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…待會兒有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有許多事情想問你 比如讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不好意思提這麼冒昧的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐看上去很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請讓她一個人靜靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是相當貴重的絕版書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你以這種價格搞得到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遊戲 CD一起送到了我們網店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不識貨真可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是有壓箱寶貝流到網上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 另一方面也有可疑的貨源進來 一身麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的情況是失竊物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送來多件未開封的相同商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上就可以隱瞞渠道清貨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到這種貨是不敢碰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕買取麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等於說店頭應該也會拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說拿貨來的人還是中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說在這裡賣了八張相同的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失竊品的可能性很高 我們不接這種買取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看不？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失竊的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問問話也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 失竊的八張CD和這個一樣沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒弄錯麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到聖櫻女學館的人會偷東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來自首了就說明還有救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自首？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 看到她穿著聖櫻女學館的校服逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就聯繫了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校稱要徹底調查呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來鬧大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後女孩子反省過了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠川 朗讀用的圖畫書準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也拜託你放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 篠川從小喜歡書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定看了許多難懂的書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候也喜歡過漫畫和兒童文學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過更對大人看的書更有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個怪孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀~怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 沒有別的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五浦 上次讀後感的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂單麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑黑是我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然上了年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是我家的寶貝狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和爺爺每天早晨送我去幼兒園
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次也聯繫我吧 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下次我去店頭取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你今天專程送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這張照片上的人是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴姐看過這張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正禁止談媽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們怎麼樣？還高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 回家好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…結衣去自首說偷了東西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號稱偷了八張同樣的CD 賣給了BOOK PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而BOOK PALACE稱沒有買下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於說沒把偷CD的事情說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說謊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過哪怕沒有賣掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷東西還是偷東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣不賣都不影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺理不清吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得原因肯定是壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校規太嚴格 不樂意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候讀了『發條橘子』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑在心底裡的東西彭地一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來沒談過麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她一直悶在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我禮拜天在家附近的公園辦自由市場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想帶她去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說髒不拉嘰的 一口回絕我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髒不拉嘰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有潔癖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說人家用過的東西髒不拉嘰的 不要碰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拉有潔癖的人去跳蚤市場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳蚤市場是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前還沒有自由市場這種潮流叫法的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潔癖？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你妹妹沒有偷東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了『發條橘子』的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於它有幾個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在家裡寫了這篇讀後感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時去圖書館嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去 人家碰過的書髒不拉嘰的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼朋友之間也不借書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完事了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼寫下的那篇讀後感？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看書寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在讀後感的開頭這麼寫道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀完這本書 我立即聽了貝多芬的第九交響曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為終章裡主人公艾力克斯聽了貝多芬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也想聽了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的刮鬍刀割開慘叫的地球臉龐 這幅景象栩栩如生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後樂章進入平緩部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後終章裡的美麗合唱即將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 那個結局很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我覺得是很可怕 很美的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有證據嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼證據？說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…寫下讀後感的人沒有真正意義上看完『發條橘子』
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託奈緒帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了這本書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？裝訂不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原版的『發條橘子』一九六二年在英國出版
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早川書房的譯本 在一九七一年刊行單行本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是它的文庫本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及這是二まま八年出版的新版
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩本不僅裝訂不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容也大相逕庭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容也？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊版裡艾力克斯的洗腦被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽貝多芬的第九交響曲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即故事在恢復惡人本性的地方收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新版在終章裡寫下了他今後的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與洗心革面的舊友重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使他主動告別暴力行為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓要成家立業做個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:23:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 『發條橘子』存在兩個結局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新版裡續寫了故事的結尾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新版的終章是讓原本寫在舊版裡的故事復活了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這才是原版的『發條橘子』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全版
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本的終章在某個階段被砍掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個階段？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個的某個階段啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國版出版的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應出版社的要求 刪除了終章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者伯吉斯因為經濟方面的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫答應了出版方的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後史丹利·庫柏力克以小說為原本 製作了電影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題越變越複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿書是庫柏力克寫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的電影影響巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便有更多的國家翻譯原本出版
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日語譯本也在一九七一年出版
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時市面上沒有收錄終章的原版
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和電影的一樣 沿襲了美國版的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來過了三十多年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在二まま八年 文庫的完全版終於出版
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的文庫本便成了絕版書
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.73,0:24:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作者的本意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯吉斯本人如何理解這件事便無從得知
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.62,0:24:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在寄予美國出版的完全版的序言裡寫道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.25,0:24:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們可以刪除寫過的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.87,0:24:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但是不可以當作沒寫過」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.52,0:25:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？等於說…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.32,0:25:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…現在書店裡只有完全版吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.53,0:25:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.61,0:25:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 你剛才說因為終章裡艾力克斯聽了貝多芬
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.66,0:25:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自己也想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.02,0:25:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全版裡還有後續
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看過這本書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.51,0:25:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看書怎麼寫的讀後感？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解釋得通的理由只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.33,0:26:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你抄了別人的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.93,0:26:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我抄了誰的讀後感？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.44,0:26:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.72,0:26:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.34,0:26:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼選了『發條橘子』？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.80,0:26:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…碰巧在書店看到它
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.21,0:26:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站附近的書店應該斷貨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.86,0:26:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你托奈緒網購了書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.63,0:26:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上順序正相反吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先看了讀後感 才對『發條橘子』有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.97,0:27:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕一開始是真的想看完書 寫下自己的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.39,0:27:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則沒必要專程找書 買書
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.98,0:27:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…事情不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.69,0:27:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不抄襲別人的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.37,0:27:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你別胡說八道啊 無憑無據的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.54,0:27:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要證據有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.87,0:27:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒？說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.48,0:27:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說在自己家裡寫了讀後感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.12,0:27:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說了不去圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.37,0:27:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.47,0:27:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀後感的原本應該在你家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.68,0:27:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菅家住第三街區
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.65,0:27:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巖谷小學畢業的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.78,0:27:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書委員田邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.57,0:27:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.77,0:27:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是結衣的同年同學
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.44,0:28:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊說兩人感情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常一起去古書店買書
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.94,0:28:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古書店？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.96,0:28:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有潔癖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.86,0:28:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說人家用過的東西髒不拉嘰的 不要碰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.66,0:28:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 結衣有潔癖
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.08,0:28:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不可能去古書店
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.52,0:28:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.98,0:28:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當朋友的應該知道她有潔癖
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.30,0:28:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯她在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.40,0:28:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝朋友麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.30,0:28:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.67,0:28:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志田說失竊的店的人看到了犯人偷東西逃跑的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.69,0:28:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.66,0:28:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著校服 看得出是聖櫻女學館的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.64,0:28:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於說店員沒有看到犯人的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.57,0:28:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.73,0:29:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.21,0:29:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.77,0:29:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣和田邊的背影很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.52,0:29:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 你沒有偷東西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當了田邊的替身而已
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.21,0:29:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有許多事情想問你 比如讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.15,0:29:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你現在讓她一個人靜靜
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.01,0:29:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊裝作和結衣感情好是為了不讓別人懷疑到自己頭上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.82,0:30:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她威脅你？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.62,0:30:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道被欺負了？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.75,0:30:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.73,0:30:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是田邊提出交易
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.38,0:30:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.77,0:30:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在DownTown Record偷CD的人是田邊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.37,0:30:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.29,0:30:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員通報給了學校 鬧得滿校風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在發無記名調查問卷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.79,0:30:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知情的人不許隱瞞 老實寫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.00,0:30:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕田邊覺得這樣下去不行 很心急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實剛才我去了巖谷小學
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.91,0:30:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.13,0:31:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊說去那邊朗讀 於是借了她圖畫書
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.26,0:31:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時在圖書室找到了讀後感文集
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.82,0:31:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校方接受你父親和大哥的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.51,0:31:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前起可以公開閱覽文集
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.75,0:31:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.93,0:31:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒說的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的讀後感作文比賽也每年受到表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.78,0:31:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比其他人寫的好多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.79,0:31:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和其他人寫的讀後感比較
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.74,0:31:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便心想或許存在類似文集的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.62,0:31:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇讀後感肯定是『發條橘子』完全版沒發行的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.18,0:31:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐或哥哥在校期間 某個人寫下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.55,0:31:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市的某個廣場上…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.30,0:31:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊在上次朗讀的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.93,0:31:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾發現了文集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.74,0:32:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有篇讀後感和結衣寫的一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.40,0:32:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴人家
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.34,0:32:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.38,0:32:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.44,0:32:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 你求我倒也可以替你保密
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.70,0:32:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.17,0:32:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對地我也有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.18,0:32:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯答應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.96,0:32:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.48,0:33:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應了田邊的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.88,0:33:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請她保密讀後感的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.20,0:33:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你抗下了偷東西的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.41,0:33:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.54,0:33:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.65,0:33:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被人當作小偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.39,0:33:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆說出來讀後感是我抄的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.79,0:33:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.60,0:33:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.66,0:33:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不出來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.47,0:33:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷別人的讀後感比什麼偷東西更加更加難為情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.34,0:33:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被人家當作抄襲
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.50,0:33:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願停學 退學！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.23,0:33:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼…抄別人的作文？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.56,0:34:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完『發條橘子』的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.57,0:34:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文章寫得非常好 讓我驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.70,0:34:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我也想看看原作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事比我想得更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.34,0:34:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有許多難懂的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.81,0:34:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果看到一半就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.98,0:34:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過寫其他書的讀後感嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.58,0:34:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.34,0:34:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這本書太難 看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.72,0:34:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.20,0:34:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.07,0:35:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和姐姐在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.52,0:35:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.70,0:35:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次看到姐姐帶著親手做的甜點出門
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.41,0:35:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想她去表白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.76,0:35:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來突然帶了許多難懂的書回來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.69,0:35:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得對方是喜歡書的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.78,0:35:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是開書店的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.41,0:35:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不不不…誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.91,0:35:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書是志田借的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？姐姐和那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.49,0:35:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.25,0:35:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 冤枉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 書是我借的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.54,0:35:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有交往啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.56,0:35:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有！你慌什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.51,0:35:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這點不說清楚我要蹲班房的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.63,0:35:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.40,0:35:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.67,0:35:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.06,0:35:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.28,0:35:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺姐姐要變得比我更懂書
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.82,0:36:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服氣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.72,0:36:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給姐姐看你能比她看更難懂的書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.15,0:36:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.29,0:36:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.99,0:36:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不會懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.32,0:36:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐從小就是大家的聚焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.94,0:36:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家總是圍著姐姐轉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.35,0:36:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.64,0:36:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少學習要超過姐姐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.44,0:36:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這點無論如何也不想輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.13,0:37:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我沒察覺到你的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.95,0:37:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.01,0:37:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.83,0:37:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯吉斯說過
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.65,0:37:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們可以刪除寫過的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.93,0:37:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但是不可以當作沒寫過」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.23,0:38:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣也不可以當作沒抄過讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.62,0:38:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該對自己做的事情負責
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.06,0:38:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真是服了她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.20,0:38:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我跟姐姐在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.77,0:38:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天大的誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.79,0:38:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 看上去像個小大人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.16,0:38:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是中學生吶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.33,0:38:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.59,0:38:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啊 有可靠的姐姐在身邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.68,0:38:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.44,0:39:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.34,0:39:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.23,0:39:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.01,0:39:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.71,0:39:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.07,0:39:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.06,0:39:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思不好意思 不好意思啊迪特裡希
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.26,0:39:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？{\fnEPSON 太明朝體Ｂ\b0\fscx62\fscy77}刊{\r}子在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.02,0:39:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說有東西要找
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.72,0:39:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.64,0:39:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.32,0:39:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.54,0:39:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 東西找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.40,0:39:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.30,0:39:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有事請要向五浦道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.01,0:39:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.07,0:40:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是篠川的讀後感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.59,0:40:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.57,0:40:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.54,0:40:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家的反應…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.30,0:40:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學生就這樣 今後長大了怎麼樣可想而知
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.98,0:40:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.73,0:40:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.47,0:40:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我沒細想就應了聲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.35,0:40:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.53,0:41:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫這篇讀後感的時候也被老師當作問題兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.17,0:41:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說寫這種讀後感的小孩子令人擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.93,0:41:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都會這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.35,0:41:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.46,0:41:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.58,0:41:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 想到這讀後感是小學生寫的的確令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.16,0:41:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不覺得是什麼壞事喲
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.42,0:41:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我在意你看完完全版的感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.33,0:41:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結尾不同 感想也不同嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.79,0:41:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.11,0:41:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話可以告訴我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.02,0:41:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來話又很長…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.21,0:42:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.70,0:42:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痊癒了的艾力克斯在完全版的最後出現
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.39,0:42:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他成長到了十八歲 放棄惡行思考著結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.29,0:42:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於只瞭解電影的人 這段故事很意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.28,0:43:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得很大喲 我替你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 老顧客了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.60,0:43:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我送書順便侃文學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.40,0:43:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我是沒戲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.28,0:43:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小心點 走好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.55,0:43:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.49,0:46:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這純粹是威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.13,0:46:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人的目的是『晚年』
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.27,0:46:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五浦很賣力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.05,0:46:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠川不在寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.94,0:46:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個奇怪的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.08,0:46:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒見過賣三百五十萬的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.30,0:46:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒聽說過要賣『晚年』啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.91,0:46:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼做種莫名其妙的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.88,0:46:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEPSON 太明朝體Ｂ\b0\fscx62\fscy77}刊{\r}子運氣不好說不定已經喪命了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.80,0:46:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要同情他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.45,0:46:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.91,0:46:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我弄出了這番是非啊

Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.48,0:44:59.37,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}故事發生在近未來超級管理社會。\N15歲的艾力克斯鍾愛暴力和音樂—
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.49,0:45:05.84,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}在他入室搶劫殺人的夜晚，同伴出賣了他。被警察逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.00,0:45:12.38,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}他在監獄中依然沒有悔改的意思。\N於是政府把他當作了人格矯正程序的實驗台。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.54,0:45:18.89,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}兩周過後，他成了害怕暴力和音樂的懦夫。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.01,0:45:25.34,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}艾力克斯重返城市，\N卻被他以前欺負過的人反過來欺負—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.52,0:45:31.87,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}他企圖自殺。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.02,0:45:38.37,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}雖然撿回一條命，可是政府畏懼社會的批判—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.53,0:45:44.91,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}把他重新變回了熱愛暴力和音樂的艾力克斯\N重新走上惡道。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.04,0:45:51.39,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}三年後，他厭倦了暴力 厭倦了自己。\N與成了家的舊友重逢—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:59.29,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,350)}像想起有一天自己也要有一個家。\N艾力克斯察覺了到自己的變化。\N故事便在這裡結束。

